{"tid":1089252,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"而家社會個個都係講禁毒","createTime":"2019-04-02T15:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T11:33:34.000Z","uid":134099,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4a34a35a422aada1b5ef05337177616b97b9b7","tid":1089252,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"坊間睇到一係就好辛苦戒毒成功嘅例子<br />\n一係就食得過量而死...<br />\n仿佛食丸仔、咳水, 大麻就只有一種可能後果, 就係死人冧樓<br />\n因為我自己都無知, 所以想上嚟請教吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知呢度會唔會有而家食開嘅巴絲可以分享吓相關經驗? <br />\n戒緊或者keep緊食都歡迎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我留低個tg方便大家搵我: <a href=\"https://t.me/meowynott\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmeowynott&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=3ba0ff08\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/meowynott</a><br />\n或者呢度傾吓先都得<br />\n而家諗緊會唔會聽完之後, 我將你嘅故事寫返喺連登講故台度, 等大家都可以理解多啲, 睇到一個更完整嘅畫面<br />\n起碼唔會見到一個人, 就淨係覺得佢係自甘墮落, 係地下泥, 唔應該存在喺呢個社會......"},{"pid":"5c4b60ecf01589e91665023acdaf77e72db00bd5","tid":1089252,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"路過嘅巴絲都可以一齊提出你嘅好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345ca6607d7db0cd9d73f92991573e3ccc48d727","tid":1089252,"uid":41355,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWGhptT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWGhptT.png&h=3c650295&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04ee0d448c59a080b56ca1aee27af21dcb49864e","tid":1089252,"uid":134099,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345ca6607d7db0cd9d73f92991573e3ccc48d727","tid":1089252,"uid":41355,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWGhptT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyW