core":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"多謝有位熱心巴打真係肯pm分享俾我知~<br />\n開心share一條佢俾我睇嘅片 (雖然我無問準過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n唔知會唔會可以有多啲嘅討論空間?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_yg3wWwRB90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_yg3wWwRB90&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=6cc6a976\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_yg3wWwRB90</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"Lsd同大麻都有試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"召喚大J 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點呀, 你今日英文DSE考成?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb2283cb4c6f802a865cee716c8124195602676","tid":1089252,"uid":75439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7e2c5377acf8fa563aeceb9b124b5c4498d1516d","tid":1089252,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7985a42d37d62475807da024decf8bc1c1b32d","tid":1089252,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"&gt;而家社會個個都係講禁毒 <br />\n香港？<br />\n外國講非刑事化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"其實我係標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然都講緊主流睇法淨係講「毒品」嘅壞處<br />\n就算外國非刑事化...都可能係講緊<br />\n「你呢班人有自由去揀一條歪路, 你要攞嚟賤, 我唔理你哋啦」<br />\n我覺得呢種講法, 都依然係貶低緊有食開嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知呀, 我視野好窄, 唔知道香港同外國有冇例外?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"Hmm...應該咁講，外國（啫係連登仔最鍾意屌嘅左膠）主流觀點唔係吸毒無害，而係：<br />\n1）大麻嘅public health effect差極都衰唔過飲酒食煙，而且太多人食，禁絕不如合法化，容易監管又有稅收，減少浪費執法資源，一舉三得。<br />\n反例係禁酒嘅伊斯蘭國家，逼個個去黑市買劣酒，政府又收唔到稅，唯一受益者係黑市網絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2）LSD/mushroom呢d較低殺傷力但無咁流行嘅drugs（類似大麻係亞洲嘅情況）好難評估社會影響，所以合唔合法化無咩所謂，唔好當街當巷食同出事（which is rare），警察都唔得閒理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3）Hard drugs(e.g opioid/meth)大家都知好危險，但聽鬼佬講落club/concert好難唔食，一個月食一次半次就問題唔大（我就唔多信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），所以問題主要係班毒蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得要禁，但都有人覺得歧視班毒蟲於事無補，反而會更令佢地戒唔到毒/唔禁反而容易監管<br />\n<br />\n理性嘅公共政策唔係講鍾唔鍾意，都唔係講「理得你死」，而係要同數據同科學考慮公共衛生同經濟影響，全部都有數可以計，但係係連登講呢d嘢好似晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09963f4b4c0ad944169ce04d8a4dcc81c52d2a63","tid":1089252,"uid":42751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"食咗LSD之後你先會明梵谷畫緊乜"},{"pid":"fce8c32c62a66ce2119c3d7ab6dfb2105c88fa54","tid":1089252,"uid":211900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e2599e5582403d716ec12ce32f2a6cd4a9e5d76","tid":1089252,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ce4bf176ab82cbf80d7c4698858c345824b30e1","tid":1089252,"uid":211900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd0f1dc3dbad3cd80210ea5e580b3579c56a7dd","tid":1089252,"uid":134099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"多謝有位熱心巴打真係肯pm分享俾我知~<br />\n開心share一條佢俾我睇嘅片 (雖然我無問準過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n唔知會唔會可以有多啲嘅討論空間?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_yg3wWwRB90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_yg3wWwRB90&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=6cc6a976\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_yg3wWwRB90</a>"},"cite